  <thing id="ipSGBlspSr" name="Blasphemous Surge" description="A blasphemous surge weapon functions as a blasphemous weapon that also casts bestow curse on a foe successfully struck with a critical hit. In addition to the normal penalty inflicted by a blasphemous weapon, a blasphemous surge weapon targets a foe hit by a critical hit with the bestow curse spell as a free actiona s if cast by the wielder of the weapon (using his level as the cleric level for the spell, his Wisdom to determine the save DC, and so on). If the weapon's critical multiplier is x3, the save DC is increased by +1, and if the multiplier is x4, the save DC is increased by +2.\n\nModerate necromancy; CL 8th; \n\n{b}Construction Requirements{/b}:  Craft Magic Arms and Armor, {i}bestow curse{/i}; Price +3 bonus.\n\n{b}Note:{/b} This thing has not been fully implemented yet." compset="ItemPower">
    <fieldval field="iPrice" value="+3"/>
    <fieldval field="iCL" value="8"/>
    <usesource source="KKBlkMagic"/>
    <tag group="iSchool" tag="Necromancy"/>
    <tag group="Helper" tag="NoPathSoc"/>
