  <thing id="ioSGTncWrt" name="Tincture of Wrath" description="Description\nThis potable has the appearance and taste of blood mixed with honey. A character drinking this fluid gains the ability to rage as a barbarian of a level equal  to one-third the drinker's level. A character already able to rage instead gains one additional rage power of his choice for which he qualifies. The duration of this ability is 1 hour, though each rage follows the normal rules for raging.\n\nA tincture of wrath is addictive, with a major addiction, Fortitude DC 20. For more information on addictions, see the Drugs and Addiction section of Chapter 8 of the GameMastery Guide. \n\n{b}Construction Requirements{/b}: Craft Wondrous Item, {i}charm person{/i}, {i}eagle's splendor{/i}; Cost: 36,400 gp\n\n{b}Note:{/b} This thing has not been fully implemented yet." compset="Wondrous">
