    <eval phase="PreLevel" priority="5000"><![CDATA[
      ~ If we're not equipped, get out now! &
      doneif (field[gIsEquip].value = 0)

      ~ Give a +6 Bonus to Str, Dex, and Con
      #enhancementbonus[hero.child[aSTR], field[abValue].value]
      #enhancementbonus[hero.child[aDEX], field[abValue].value]
      #enhancementbonus[hero.child[aCON], field[abValue].value]

      ~ Give Fast Healing 1
      #applybonus[abValue,hero.childfound[xFastHeal],field[abValue2].value]

      ~ Set situational penalty on will save
      #situational[hero.child[svWill], signed(field[abValue3].value) & " penalty vs your master." , field[name].text]]]></eval>
    </thing>
  <thing id="irSGRngWhs" name="Ring of Whispers" description="Description\nThese rings come in matched sets, with one black silver and the other white gold. The price is for a set. The two creatures wearing the rings gain a +10 competence bonus on Bluff checks made to pass secret messages to each other. \n\nBecause of their popularity among criminals, spies, and rebels, many jurisdictions outlaw these rings. Others restrict them to use among an official order \nof secret peacekeepers, who might well have sets of 4, 6, or 8 matched rings (+1,000 gp to the value of a set for each additional ring in a set).\n\n{b}Construction Requirements{/b}: Craft Magic Ring, {i}whispering wind{/i}; Cost: 2,500 gp\n\n{b}Note:{/b} This thing has not been fully implemented yet." compset="Ring" lotsize="2">
